definitions.definition: A ceremonial county of England , the most northerly county of England bordered by County Durham , Cumbria , Tyne and Wear , Scotland and the North Sea .
A unitary authority of the county of Northumberland , England , which includes all of the traditional county except the area around Newcastle upon Tyne .
